=== STEP 1: DSERS (AliExpress / Electronics) ===
App: DSers‑AliExpress Dropshipping
URL: https://apps.shopify.com/dsers
Setup:
1. Install DSers from App Store
2. Connect your AliExpress account
3. Search products: electronics, audio, smart home
4. Import products with 1-click
5. DSers auto-fulfils orders when customers buy

Best product categories for AU:
- Smart home devices (plugs, bulbs, cameras)
- TWS earbuds & headphones
- Phone accessories & chargers
- Laptop accessories
- Gaming peripherals

Pricing formula: AliExpress cost × 3 = AUD retail price
(covers: product + shipping + Shopify fees + profit)

=== STEP 2: SPOCKET (AU Local Suppliers) ===
App: Spocket ‑ US & EU Dropshipping
URL: https://apps.shopify.com/spocket
Setup:
1. Install Spocket
2. Filter by: Ship from Australia / New Zealand
3. Categories: fitness equipment, health monitors, wellness
4. Import products with branded invoicing
5. Faster AU delivery (3-7 days vs 14-20 for AliExpress)

Best for:
- Fitness trackers & smartwatches
- Yoga & meditation accessories
- Sleep monitors & white noise machines
- Wellness gadgets

=== STEP 3: ZENDROP (Pet Tech) ===
App: Zendrop ‑ Dropshipping & POD
URL: https://apps.shopify.com/zendrop
Setup:
1. Install Zendrop
2. Search: pet GPS, pet camera, automatic feeder
3. Enable branded packaging (add FutureTek logo)
4. Set AU as primary market
5. Enable auto-fulfilment

Best for:
- Pet GPS trackers & collars
- Automatic pet feeders & water dispensers  
- Pet cameras (treat dispensing)
- Smart pet doors
- Health monitoring collars

=== STEP 4: SHOPIFY SETTINGS FOR AUSTRALIA ===
Required settings (do these in Shopify Admin):

1. Settings → Store details → Store address: Australia
2. Settings → Payments → Shopify Payments (AU) → Enable
3. Settings → Payments → Alternative payments → Add AfterPay/Clearpay
4. Settings → Markets → Primary market → Australia
5. Settings → Currencies → Australian Dollar (AUD) → Default
6. Settings → Taxes → Australia → Enable GST (10%)
7. Settings → Shipping → Add Australian shipping zones
8. Settings → Legal → Add AU-compliant privacy policy & refund policy

=== STEP 5: SHIPPING ZONES (AUSTRALIA) ===
Create these zones in Settings → Shipping:
- Australia - Standard (5-14 days): $9.95 (free over $100)
- Australia - Express (2-5 days): $14.95
- New Zealand - Standard (7-14 days): $14.95
- International - Standard (14-30 days): $19.95

=== STEP 6: AFTERPAY SETUP ===
1. Go to: https://www.afterpay.com/en-AU/business
2. Sign up as AU merchant
3. Get Afterpay credentials
4. In Shopify: Settings → Payments → Add payment method → AfterPay
5. Add AfterPay widget to product pages (auto with Shopify Payments)

=== STEP 7: ABN & GST ===
For selling in Australia:
1. Register for ABN: https://www.abr.gov.au
2. Register for GST (required if turnover > $75k AUD)
3. Add ABN to invoices and store footer
4. Shopify auto-calculates 10% GST for AU customers
